2. record
(1)upgrade g++ to 4.8.2 from 4.1.2
[Refrence]http://www.21ops.com/linux/14922.html
* notify: the g++ 4.8.2 is in /usr/local/bin, but not in /usr/bin./usr/bin/g++ is also 4.1.2
(2)compile commond must add parameter: -std=c++11
